headline: The Best High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy for 2025 and Beyond
summary: Investors are looking for solid dividend stocks with volatility returning to the markets.  Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO) has historically weathered recessions well.  It has increased the dividend for 63 consecutive years after recently increasing its quarterly payment by 5% to $0.51.
